Package com.nequissimus.university.k1584.ui.actions

Provides UI actions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddNewPlaceAction
    Action to add a new place to the net.
    AddNewTransitionAction
    Action to add new transitions to the net.
    CanvasChangeSizeAction
    This abstract action helps implement actions that will resize the canvas.
    CanvasLargerAction
    Action that will cause the canvas to be extended.
    CanvasSmallerAction
    Action that will cause the canvas to become smaller.
    ChangeIconSizeAction
    This action changes the size for all objects on the canvas.
    CloseWindowAction
    Action called when trying to close the window via the window menu bar.
    ConnectArrowAction
    Action used to connect a label with another one.
    CreateMarkingAction
    Action for creating a new marking.
    CreateSnapshotAction
    Action for creating a new snapshot.
    DecreaseMarkingsAction
    Action for decreasing the number of markings on a place.
    DeleteMarkingAction
    Action for deleting markings.
    DeleteSnapshotAction
    Action for deleting a snapshot.
    DisconnectArrowAction
    Action that disconnects a label from another one.
    IncreaseMarkingsAction
    Action for increasing the number of markings on a place.
    LoadFileAction
    Action called when trying to load a file.
    OccurTransitionAction
    Action that makes an event on a given transition occur.
    RemoveObjectAction
    Remove all selected objects from the canvas and logical net.
    If no object has been selected explicitly, the one the action has been executed on will be removed.
    RenameMarkingAction
    Action for renaming markings.
    RenameObjectAction
    Action that allows the user to rename a given label object.
    RenameSnapshotAction
    Action that lets the user choose the snapshot to be renamed and then opens a dialog for the user to enter the new name.
    ResetApplicationAction
    Action that resets the entire application, logic and UI.
    SaveFileAction
    Action called when trying to save a file.
    SelectMarkingAction
    Select a marking for the current net.
    SelectSnapshotAction
    Action for selecting an active snapshot.
    TokenLargerAction
    Action called when trying to increase the token size.
    TokenSmallerAction
    Action called when trying to decrease the token size.
